property.name: note
property.value:
global_phase1: - Set to 1 to move to phase 1 fight - If set to 1 when event starts, music will immediately go to transition music leading into phase 1 fight
global_phase1_idle: - Set to 1 to crossfade to phase 1 idle
global_dissonance: - Set to 1 to move to dissonance phase
global_dissonance_idle: - Set to 1 to crossfade to dissonance idle phase.
global_fight_outro: - Set to 1 to move to fight outro sequence
